When four artists set the stage on fire — Noida listened!
On 22nd June, DLF Mall of India turned into a full-blown concert arena as Kutle Khan, Ritesh Prasanna, Vinayak Pant, and Bobby Pathak lit the stage on fire. 🔥

From folk fusion to soul-stirring sounds —
World Music Day in Noida wasn’t just heard, it was felt.

This wasn’t just a performance.
It was Noida singing, swaying, and standing still… all at once. 💫

Let the music take over 🎶
This World Music Day, DLF Mall of India turns into a stage for magic ✨
From rising stars to seasoned voices — feel the rhythm, vibe with the beats, and lose yourself in melodies that’ll move you 🎤🎧🎵
Only with Buskr.

📅 Date: 22nd June
⏰ Timings: 6 PM onwards
📍 Location: Central Atrium, DLF Mall of India

Follow @whatshappening365 for more updates ▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️
